- **DA-12 "direction failure" зёәпҪ®иҚіпҪ»иқ—пЈ° = backend confound** (Ollama з«Ҡгғ»SGLang иңҠеҖЎеіЎзёәпҪ§
  Vendi +2.144 / Burrows +5.391)
- **LoRA effect proper baseline** (rank=8 no-LoRA SGLang vs LoRA-on SGLang) зёәпҪҜ
  near-zero: Vendi +0.446 / Burrows -0.960
